room_title: Escape room "CDC Lockdown" by Urban Escape Games in Atlanta

room_description: The CDC is on lockdown! You weren't even supposed to be here, but you stayed behind after the tour to chat with the guide and now they're not letting anyone out... What could it be? As the events unravel, you must take charge and find a way to save your lives. In an hour it will be too late.
